    "Id": "chassisdef_thresher_mk_ii_THR2-1",
    "Name": "Thresher Mk II",
    "Details": "The 'Mech features a 300-rated XL engine with MASC and a Supercharger, allowing it to reach high speeds normally found on lighter machines. Enhancing its mobility further are five jump jets, giving it a jump capacity of 150 meters. The Thresher Mk II's armament features a mix of long range and short range options. Its main battery of guns consists of an ER PPC with a LRM-15, supplied with two tons of ammunition. At shorter ranges, a large pulse laser coupled with a SRM-4 and flamer are available for use. Its ammunition is protected by CASE II, greatly decreasing damage to the right torso from ammo explosions and allowing the XL engine to continue operating with little fear of damage. Clan Sea Fox chose to protect the 'Mech with 9.5 tons of Gamma Special Reflective armor. This armor gives the 'Mech resistance to energy weapons, but makes it more vulnerable to artillery and some ballistic weapons.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Targeting - Medium</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.12</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Left Lower</color>",
